### Test Write Pipeline Performance Optimization
### Target: <10s for simple INSERT operations

@baseUrl = https://localhost:7189
@token = {{$dotenv BEARER_TOKEN}}

### TEST 1: Simple INSERT - "Add a new customer named John Smith"
### Expected: 7-10s (down from 12-20s)
### Should use PreResolvedEntities from IntentClassifier
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/agent/process/stream
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Add a new customer named John Smith",
  "connectionId": "{{$dotenv CONNECTION_ID}}",
  "conversationId": null
}

