### TEST 5: Complex INSERT with FK - "Add a new order for customer John Smith"
### Expected: 10-15s (needs FK lookup)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/agent/process/stream
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Add a new order for customer John Smith with product Laptop",
  "connectionId": "{{$dotenv CONNECTION_ID}}",
  "conversationId": null
}

